{"tid":1861697,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩可唔可以用UV燈/殺菌機消毒","createTime":"2020-02-04T08:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T13:56:18.000Z","uid":145428,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"35153020bef6186712bd157f1ad01b3514d6d70a","tid":1861697,"uid":145428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"罩又搶唔到<br />\n窮撚無錢買<br />\n<br />\n重用口罩變得無可厚非<br />\n唔知可唔可以咁消毒？"},{"pid":"340fda4c843163d48863dc832463f1bde76f1adc","tid":1861697,"uid":261627,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:51:51.000Z","msg":"要咖瑪射線"},{"pid":"620d25511db251cf757b5a43589a4352eaa634b6","tid":1861697,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:51:54.000Z","msg":"曬太陽都得"},{"pid":"e48d1a8263a263a7a3dcb5b44c82696f6ca11acd","tid":1861697,"uid":23511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】面對全球出現「口罩荒」，專家呼籲各界謹慎使用，亦千萬不要囤積，否則產量再多也應付不來。專家亦多次提醒民眾即棄口罩不能重用。<br />\n<br />\n內地《科技日報》訪問了，曾參與「抗沙士防護紡織品研製」項目的專家靳向煜。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，雖然官方明確指出攝氏56度下待三十分鐘可有效消滅病毒，但不能以清蒸或水煮方式循環再用口罩，原因是過瀘層主要由聚丙烯熔噴超細纖維構成。這些材料會經過處理，使其帶有微量的電荷，增加過瀘層在蓬鬆環境下仍能保持吸附力，清蒸和水煮會令電荷消失，超細纖維亦不耐高溫，會收縮變形影響防護功效。<br />\n<br />\n至於以火酒消毒，由於口罩表面都經過「抗水處理」，火酒難以消毒口罩內部，而且會影響口罩外層防水結構。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">利用紫外線燈消毒一樣不可行，因為聚丙烯熔噴材料對紫外線非常敏感，紫外線會破壞它的結構，減低口罩過濾能力。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=379288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379288&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlG2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=bde73e41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379288&h=d436136a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=379288</a>"},{"pid":"4ea5825819a9a10a286119960c8aebe93c56c741","tid":1861697,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:56:25.000Z","msg":"好似話紫外線會破壞膠質 降低防護效果<br />\n但好過冇口罩？"},{"pid":"f7c6e91e5cc2375f068cac68b751ef3895e76152","tid":1861697,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ea5825819a9a10a286119960c8aebe93c56c741","tid":1861697,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:56:25.000Z","msg":"好似話紫外線會破壞膠質 降低防護效果<br />\n但好過冇口罩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"用 乾衣機/暖風機又得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3438ea8c43e143f6e57693f61cd709f0140fe5","tid":1861697,"uid":41355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"好似研究過話gamma ray係唯一可行既方法"},{"pid":"3dd949bbd7039ff23fba25ab20f7ba826d0d6188","tid":1861697,"uid":31405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f7c6e91e5cc2375f068cac68b751ef3895e76152","tid":1861697,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ea5825819a9a10a286119960c8aebe93c56c741","tid":1861697,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:56:25.000Z","msg":"好似話紫外線會破壞膠質 降低防護效果<br />\n但好過冇口罩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"用 乾衣機/暖風機又得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"一吹既咩菌咩病毒都即刻飛起晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cc8a77aa5c244a89c4c5369eddd87192b7e3db","tid":1861697,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:05:07.000Z","msg":"原來口罩都係高科技野..."},{"pid":"1a73601835ecfa17764753b6ceaf5e09c7bfeebf","tid":1861697,"uid":145428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:21:02.000Z","msg":"收到<br />\n<br />\n所以口罩係無方法重用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39aad2b3b0b038096151e55fa7130d74f6fe46eb","tid":1861697,"ui